profile:
Home Painters Toronto

If you're looking for a professional painting and home renovation company with years of experience to prove it, then look no further, Home Painters Toronto is the contractor for you. We specialize in interior, exterior, residential, and commercial painting and our services don't stop there! We can also help you with drywall repair and installation, plaster, stucco ceiling repair and removal, carpentry, Kitchen Cabinet repainting, hardwood flooring and much more! Call one of our customer service experts now and be well on your way to a quote and a beautifully transformed property.

Serving Toronto and the regional Municipalities of York, Halton, Peel, Durham, and more!   

Remember when you go with Home Painters we value your business and referrals and are committed to getting it done right the first time. GUARANTEED!

Why use Home Painters to paint your house/office?
•Two Year Guarantee On All Work Done
•Full Workers Compensation
•5 Million Liability Insurance
•Fully Bonded Workers (Criminal Background Checks on ALL Workers)
•30 Years Experience in the Painting Industry
•Thousands of Satisfied Clients
•Top Quality Paints Used Including Benjamin Moore, Dulux, Behr, Sherwin Williams, Para etc
•Drop sheets to Protect Your Floors and Belongings
•100% Satisfaction Guaranteed!!

 Interior Painting Services Include:
•Painting (i.e. walls, trim, doors, floors, ceilings, etc.)
•Staining (i.e. banisters, hardwood floors, cabinets, etc.)
•Faux finishing  
•Stucco Painting and Repair
•Wallpapering and Removal 
•Drywall Repair and Replacement
•Plaster

 Exterior Painting Services Include:
•Painting Exterior Surfaces (ie. windows, brick, doors, eaves, soffits, aluminum siding, etc.)
•Deck/Fence Staining and Refinishing
•Power Washing 
•Caulking 
•Rotten Wood Replacement/Repair

profile:
Smooth Ceiling Ltd
Smooth Ceiling specializes in removing stipple, other know as stucco/popcorn from your ceilings. 
Our team take pride in the work we do and we ourselves on making sure we get the job done right, and on your time schedule. Each area is covered and protected from floor to ceiling to ensure that dust does not seep through out the house. We specialize in turning your stucco ceiling to a smooth and perfect finish. 
We're dedicated to providing you the resources and services you need to modernize your home., 
We remove your outdated popcorn ceiling in a fast, clean and efficient manner.
Acoustic ceiling also known as the "popcorn ceiling" was in fashion over thirty years ago, but now new houses do not have these ceilings unless you request it prior to a new home being built.
Many home owners are also removing the stipple in their homes for benefits such as

Many benefits to the removal of Popcorn/Acoustic Ceilings:
	•	Brightens the room 
	•	Increase Re-sale Value
	•	Damage Control
        •	Modernizes the look      
	•	Less Dust and les Spider Webs
	•	Cleaner, Professional Look
	•	And much more…

Popcorn Ceiling Removal / Stucco Removal - Painting - Water Damaged Ceilings - Drywall Repairs - Pot Lights- Crown Moulding-Custom Kitchens-Custom Closets

brands: Smooth Ceiling Ltd works with the highest quality of material such as  Benjamin Moore CGC plaster, Anchore protective Paper etc
specialities: We specialize in transforming your rough outdated ceiling into a  work of art.  We make sure that we meet your budget and time line. We protect your floors and walls from top to bottom to ensure that the dust does not seep into other rooms nor your furnace. We close off your vents and air intakes.  We use a wet method to remove the stucco "popcorn", then apply multiple coats of plaster to you're ceiling to insure the stability and longevity. We then use an LED to double check for any imperfections we might of missed. We feather sand the ceiling to a smooth finish and proceed by priming and painting the project with a top Benjamin Moore prime and paint. We finish the job by cleaning the work area and disposing the garbage.

profile:
With over 12 years of experience,your acoustic ceiling removal job is sure to be done right by the Popcorn Ceiling Removers. We are fully insured with 2 million liability and WSIB for your peace of mind. We are dedicated to providing our customers with top quality drywall and painting services. We can remove your outdated popcorn ceilings and replace with a completely smooth finish, install potlights, install crown moulding, and even paint your entire home. When you need a company with years of experience and a company you can depend on and trust, we say you can depend on us.

Popcorn ceiling removal is not cheap, but not expensive either. We have mastered the removal process and have been able to lower our prices to meet the more stricter of budgets. Many times, 
our crew can complete your popcorn ceiling removal and re-texture in as little as one day! When your ready to remove your popcorn ceilings and obtain a competitive quote by a company that has been in the business of removing popcorn ceilings for over a decade, well then you are at the right place!

Owner – Benny Leigh

I served my time as an apprentice plasterer in Ireland achieving an NVQ Level 2, a certificate in EIFS Technician, and successfully ran my own plastering business for many years. profile:
Kris's Painting offers full service paint, stucco removal (popcorn ceiling removal), plaster & wallpaper services to meet any need. 
We offer a high quality painting services that are guaranteed to be professional, friendly, clean and done on time!!
 
We offer both residential and commercial services including 

****

* Painting, wall preparation, priming and colour changes
* Plastering, fixing all cracks are nail holes before paint is applied
* Drywall Repairs, from flood and water damage to new pot light installation damage
* Stucco Removal (popcorn ceiling removal) to modernize your space and add value to your home
* Wallpaper Removal and reapplication of new paper or preparation for paint
* Mold Removal on drywall or plaster walls. We always use an Air Scrubber to ensure no airborne particles are released in your home environment. Safety is our number one concern. 
* Basement Flood Repair normally requires a minimum removal of the bottom two feet of drywall, insulation and baseboard replacement and reinstall. 
* Power Washing is recommended before applying new paint or stain to exterior decks, siding and brick. 
 
Each projects is different and will receive a specific quote based on your needs. 
At Kris's Painting we always strive for 100% satisfaction for your project.

profile:
POPCORN CEILING/STUCCO REMOVAL:

When you think of a modern interior in a home, popcorn ceilings usually don’t make the cut. In fact, popcorn ceilings usually make a home look dated and unattractive.

Instead, a smooth ceiling has the opposite effect: it can enhance the look of a home’s interior and give it a more modern finish and feel.
But what can you do if your home has popcorn ceilings? Whether you’re looking to improve the aesthetics of your home for your own purposes or are looking to give your home a boost before selling it, removing your popcorn ceilings in favor of a smooth ceiling can make a massive difference in the look of your home.

Luckily, removing popcorn ceilings and opting for a smooth ceiling instead is as easy as making the call to professionals in popcorn ceiling removal. 
 (  These are just some of the reasons why you should upgrade your ceilings)
                  
To eliminate falling white specs
To increase your resale value
Popcorn ceilings are old-fashioned
Popcorn ceilings trap allergens
Popcorn ceilings are a breeding ground for dust-mites and spiders
They bring down the height of the ceiling
Makes room appear darker as the texture absorbs shadows from light
Makes house look modern

Let The AK PLASTERING in TORONTO transform your out dated popcorn ceilings into smooth, modern masterpieces!

The Services We Provide :

Popcorn Ceiling /Stucco Removal
--------------------------------------
Plastering -Taping

profile:
Alsoufi Contractors specializes in the DUST-FREE removal of popcorn (stucco/stipple) ceiling and its FULL-FINISH. 

Our standard of work entails our process to remove the popcorn, plaster all necessary sections, sand (DUST-FREE) till smooth, and paint using Benjamine Moore paints, for a perfect smooth white ceiling. All required surfaces are covered and protected from floor to ceiling to ensure the dust does not cover your furniture. 

We take precise measurements for our quotes for FREE and provide a price on the spot to make the process simple and concise. We specify the time budget and necessary precautions and fully commit to our agreement. 

Removal of your popcorn ceiling : 

-Expands your space
-brightens the area
-Complements Pot lights in the ceiling
-Increase property value 
-Reduces dust formation
-Modernizes home
